title: Etsy Trend Radar: Q1 2026 Design Strategy
summary: Etsy continues strong growth with new AI discovery tools. Our Q1 2026 strategy focuses on immediate opportunities in Dopamine Gifting and personalization, evolving into Spring's Island Luxe and Messy Coquette aesthetics. Prepare for a deeper dive into nostalgic styles and superfandom, leveraging Etsy's trend reports for sustained success.
